{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778976434334,"sessionID":"ses_1ccbfceb9ffenpdxiMuCe2grdL","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_UfqtIuGfjQ03nfFos8avK0Fs","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+Updated the existing `occlusal surface of tooth` term (`UBERON:8600149`) with the requested synonyms and attribution metadata. Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+## Summary\n+\n+This updates the existing `occlusal surface of tooth` term (`UBERON:8600149`) in response to issue #3631.\n+\n+## Changes\n+\n+- Added `chewing surface` as a related synonym.\n+- Added `masticatory surface` as a related synonym.\n+- Added the missing contributor ORCID `https://orcid.org/0009-0002-7282-0836`.\n+- Added a `term_tracker_item` link back to `https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3631`.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The requested anatomical structure already existed as `UBERON:8600149`, with the requested parent `tooth surface structure` (`UBERON:8600148`) and an appropriate definition citing the supplied dental surface references. I therefore updated the existing term rather than creating a duplicate.\n+\n+## Completed Checklist\n+\n+- Read imported issue context from `__issue_context__.json`.\n+- Checked the requested parent term and existing tooth surface terms using `obo-grep.pl`.\n+- Confirmed that `occlusal surface of tooth` already exists as `UBERON:8600149`.\n+- Applied edits through the `terms/` checkout/checkin workflow.\n+- Verified the new ORCID resolves through ORCID's public API.\n+- Verified the supplied dental surface references are reachable and relevant to occlusal tooth surfaces.\n+- Reserialized and syntax-validated `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert`.\n+- Committed only `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` locally.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,1 @@\n+Updated the existing `occlusal surface of tooth` term (`UBERON:8600149`) with the requested synonyms and attribution metadata. Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nIndex: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,25 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+This updates the existing `occlusal surface of tooth` term (`UBERON:8600149`) in response to issue #3631.\n+\n+## Changes\n+\n+- Added `chewing surface` as a related synonym.\n+- Added `masticatory surface` as a related synonym.\n+- Added the missing contributor ORCID `https://orcid.org/0009-0002-7282-0836`.\n+- Added a `term_tracker_item` link back to `https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3631`.\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The requested anatomical structure already existed as `UBERON:8600149`, with the requested parent `tooth surface structure` (`UBERON:8600148`) and an appropriate definition citing the supplied dental surface references. I therefore updated the existing term rather than creating a duplicate.\n+\n+## Completed Checklist\n+\n+- Read imported issue context from `__issue_context__.json`.\n+- Checked the requested parent term and existing tooth surface terms using `obo-grep.pl`.\n+- Confirmed that `occlusal surface of tooth` already exists as `UBERON:8600149`.\n+- Applied edits through the `terms/` checkout/checkin workflow.\n+- Verified the new ORCID resolves through ORCID's public API.\n+- Verifi