fore updated the existing term rather than creating a duplicate.\n+\n+## Completed Checklist\n+\n+- Read imported issue context from `__issue_context__.json`.\n+- Checked the requested parent term and existing tooth surface terms using `obo-grep.pl`.\n+- Confirmed that `occlusal surface of tooth` already exists as `UBERON:8600149`.\n+- Applied edits through the `terms/` checkout/checkin workflow.\n+- Verified the new ORCID resolves through ORCID's public API.\n+- Verified the supplied dental surface references are reachable and relevant to occlusal tooth surfaces.\n+- Reserialized and syntax-validated `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert`.\n+- Committed only `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` locally.\n","additions":25,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778976434325,"end":1778976434332}},"id":"prt_e3342061a001iTG7Jnd98uFyyk","sessionID":"ses_1ccbfceb9ffenpdxiMuCe2grdL","messageID":"msg_e3341fe5d001e2AqpkFkMJwvjk"}}
